trugatz wondered aloud if Glossier will find a buyer in =E2=80=9925; John O=
urand relayed a Netflix sports rights shocker; and Marion Maneker got to th=
e bottom of the Sotheby=E2=80=99s nightmare. Meanwhile, Peter Hamby evaluat=
ed the contours of the Democrats=E2=80=99 post-MSNBC playbook, and Tara Pal=
meri contemplated the limits of
Trump=E2=80=99s executive power.

