<strong>Bill</strong>, <strong>Eleanor</strong>, the famous image of <stron=
g>Lincoln</strong>, and both portrayals of <strong>Kennedy=E2=80=94</strong=
>the one painted before that day in Dallas, and the subsequent one with his=
